<h2>Career's at Hotelplan</h2>
<p>Inghams was founded by Walter Ingham in 1934 and specialises in ski holidays, walking holidays and holidays to Lapland. Walter was passionate about sharing all that our amazing planet has to offer with others from around Britain, be it cruising down a slope on skis, chasing the Northern lights on a sleigh or walking to the best view points across Europe. We aim to carry on that sense of adventure in all our holidays to this day.</p>
<p>If you're looking for a career that's not just a job but a fulfilling adventure, we welcome you to explore opportunities with us. Join our team and be part of a dynamic, purpose-driven business dedicated to making a positive impact in the world.</p>
